      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for this. it's a good start. can we make it a little less generic though? could you add a sentence or two that acknowledges how tough the decision was for the hiring team specifically because of their strong technical performance? i just want it to feel a bit more personal so they don't feel like they're getting a canned response.",
